{"tid":2231350,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教育局：首次有小學教師教材涉散播港獨　取消其教師註冊","createTime":"2020-10-05T14:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T15:01:23.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2dbf3d2d4aa648c10ea135a2daafba08aaf79c42","tid":2231350,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:51:32.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】教育局表示，一名小學教師的教案、教料等有計劃地散播港獨信息，決定取消他的教師註冊，是首次有老師因社會事件而被取消注冊。<br />\n<br />\n教育局表示經詳細調查，認爲該教師嚴重專業失德，設計的校本教案、教學材料和工作紙有計劃地散播「港獨」信息，不符合特區在《基本法》下的憲制和法律地位；指很明顯在課堂散播「港獨」信息，不是一時疏忽，當中不少內容屬扭曲和偏頗，對學生構成嚴重的損害。<br />\n<br />\n局方亦已就校長、副校長的監管不力發出譴責信，亦向其他沒有考慮教學內容是否恰當，而使用教案和教材的教師發出書面警告。"},{"pid":"2d67af9dd22a2721be0f18539282042d7c4f8167","tid":2231350,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:51:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/36991\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F36991&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL1znTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=48e6df35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F36991&h=2fd4dc56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/36991</a>"},{"pid":"4cdba15cb4147a090137340bf21d32cec516d16d","tid":2231350,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T15:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}